Introduction

ACID EYES was the third sub-unit of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS.

On June 1, 2023, tripleS announced their newly formed unit, ACID EYES, by posting a release schedule on their SNS. This unit, not decided by a Gravity (tripleS' voting event), is a special unit consisting of the members of their two previous sub-units: Acid Angel from Asia and +(KR)ystal Eyes. These members are YooYeon, NaKyoung, SeoYeon, ChaeYeon, YuBin, JiWoo, HyeRin and SooMin.

ACID EYES debuted on July 6, 2023, with the single album "Cherry Gene".
